name: The Gilded Archon
description:
The Gilded Archon claims sovereignty over all of the Tapestry.
Both king and god of his people, the perpetually armored Gaunts, he wages war against anyone who refuses to bow down to his rule, be it dreamer or denizen, and constantly seeks to expand the borders of his empire.
Few believe he could ever accomplish such a goal or challenge the true powers of the realm of realms, but only the bravest don’t tremble at the approach of his monstrous armies and his terrible war machines.
